    <briefdescription>
<para>Symplectic-Euler integrator for free rigid-body states. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Uses semi-implicit integration: velocities are updated first from forces, then positions/orientations are advanced using updated velocities. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
